  <h1>🚀 AI Tools Hub</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">A simple website built with Bootstrap 5 to showcase useful AI tools.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>🏠 Home Page</h2>
  <img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f218b09a-2fcd-48c7-8dc1-63c4db6a07c2" alt="Home Page" class="img">

  <h2>🚀 Hero Section</h2>
  <img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9758584a-fe15-432c-9a11-638d6b2c0670" alt="Hero Section" class="img">

  <h2>📋 Project Overview</h2>
  <p>
    This project is my submission for the Bootstrap 5 Internship Task.
    It is a responsive multi-page website that lists useful AI tools.
  </p>

  <h2>🌐 Live Demo</h2>
  <p>
    <a href="https://ai-tools-hub1.vercel.app" target="_blank">
      View Live Project
    </a>
  </p>

  <h2>📁 Pages Included</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Home (index.html)</b> – Hero section, search bar, filters, and tool cards</li>
    <li><b>About (about.html)</b> – Project overview and purpose</li>
    <li><b>Contact (contact.html)</b> – Contact form with basic validation</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>🛠️ Technologies Used</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>HTML</li>
    <li>CSS</li>
    <li>Bootstrap 5 (via CDN)</li>
    <li>Bootstrap Icons</li>
    <li>JavaScript (search, filter, form handling)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>✨ Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Responsive design (mobile, tablet, desktop)</li>
    <li>Search functionality</li>
    <li>Category filters (Writing, Coding, Design)</li>
    <li>Card-based layout with hover effects</li>
    <li>Sticky navigation bar</li>
    <li>Clean hero section</li>
    <li>Contact form with success message</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>🧠 Learning & Reflection</h2>

  <h3>How I built this project</h3>
  <p>
    I started by exploring Bootstrap documentation and example components to understand how they work.
    Instead of copying full templates, I selected useful components and combined them to build my own layout.
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>Created the navigation bar</li>
    <li>Designed the Home page layout</li>
    <li>Built the tools section using cards</li>
    <li>Added search and filter using JavaScript</li>
    <li>Created About and Contact pages</li>
    <li>Improved layout using custom CSS</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Use of AI Tools</h3>
  <p>
    I used AI tools like ChatGPT and Grok for fixing issues and making small improvements.
    I also referred to Bootstrap documentation.
    The overall structure and implementation were done by me.
  </p>

  <h3>Challenges Faced</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Getting search and filter to work properly together</li>
    <li>Maintaining consistent design across pages</li>
    <li>Keeping the UI simple and clean</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>What I Learned</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>How to use Bootstrap components effectively</li>
    <li>How to build responsive layouts</li>
    <li>How to combine HTML, CSS, and JavaScript</li>
    <li>Importance of clean UI design</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>⏱️ Time Taken</h2>
  <p>Approximately <b>10–12 hours</b></p>

  <h2>🚀 How to Run Locally</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Clone the repository</li>
    <li>Open <b>index.html</b> in your browser</li>
    <li>No installation required (uses CDN)</li>
  </ol>

  <hr>

  <p class="footer">
    This project helped me improve my frontend skills, especially working with Bootstrap and layout design.
  </p>

